      "value": "<p>Your moth releases a shower of dust to reveal your foes. Until the start of your next turn, if you damage a @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Concealed]{Concealed} or @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Hidden]{Hidden} creature in your moth's reach with a Strike, that creature requires only a <span data-pf2-check=\"flat\" data-pf2-traits=\"concealed\" data-pf2-label=\"\" data-pf2-dc=\"3\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"all\">Flat Check</span> to target it if it's concealed, or <span data-pf2-check=\"flat\" data-pf2-traits=\"hidden\" data-pf2-label=\"\" data-pf2-dc=\"9\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"all\">Flat Check</span> if it's hidden. The reduced DC lasts until the end of your next turn.</p>"
